<#a5755bf645b86b828c2c79bf95f88fc0> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/a47932fd-8b6a-47cd-a8e7-429f3c750bdc>;
