<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#61fd18f58a01e5a53fbde746a2d6bb9a>.
<#61fd18f58a01e5a53fbde746a2d6bb9a> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <https://opendata-catalog.smhi.se/md/ed59a575-570a-412b-86c8-01d2e37ffbaf>;
