    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/publisher> <http://dataportal.se/organisation/SE2021002817>;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/description> "Green Chromatic Index (GCI) also known as Green Chromatic Coordinate (GCC) is a measure of the greenness of vegetation.  It is calculated from daily averaged RGB (Red, Green, Blue) composites values of digital images captured by PhenoCams.\nRöbäcksdalen Field Research Station (2022). Phenocam - Green Chromatic Coordinates (GCC) Composite Image Mean Values from Röbäcksdalen Research Area, Mast 10m Phenocam 01, 2019-04-11–2019-10-23 [Data set]. Swedish Infrastructure for Ecosystem Science (SITES). https://hdl.handle.net/11676.1/1qdZf0igVpGYgCu7Kqe_cZox"@en;
    <http://purl.org/dc/terms/temporal> _:b0__1139.
_:b0__1139 <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#endDate> "2019-10-23"^^<http://www.w3.org/2001/XMLSchema#dateTime>;
