<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#51ef464f11d6b61d528914f9baaea816>.
<#51ef464f11d6b61d528914f9baaea816> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N23593>;
