<feed> <https://w3id.org/tree#member> <#0ef5861a08d43e77f09fe67108206196>.
<#0ef5861a08d43e77f09fe67108206196> a <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#Update>;
    <https://www.w3.org/ns/activitystreams#object> <http://api.kolada.se/v3/kpi/N02369>;
