<https://doi.org/10.5878/001858> <http://www.w3.org/ns/dcat#keyword> "yngre järnålder"@sv, "Late Iron Age"@en, "medeltid"@sv, "Middle Ages"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/ns/prov#qualifiedAttribution> _:b0__74891.
